<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:26.0pt; ">Privacy Policy</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Information  Collection:</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">We will collect basic information when you register  for an account to use for VigilantEye.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">When using our site, you may be asked to enter your  E-mail address and/or name.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Anonymous access to the website is allowed, however,  features will be limited</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Information  Usage:</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Information collected from the users will be used to  personalize the users&rsquo; account</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Send updates about website information and  application information</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Personalize experience when using the application and  website features</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Information  Protection:</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">We implement secure practice of website and database  security. If you would like to know more about your protection, you may send an  E-mail to </span><a href="mailto:cvg@sfu.ca"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">cvg@sfu.ca</span></a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Outside  Parties Information Disclosure:</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">We will never sell, trade, or give out your personal  information to outside parties without your knowledge and consent. We will only  release personal information to trusted third parties that assists in the  operation of the website. We may also release information to comply with the  law, the RCMP, and protect our rights and others&rsquo; rights, property, and safety.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Other non-personal information visitor information  may be provided to other parties for other uses such as website traffic information.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">By using our site, you agree to our privacy policy&rsquo;s  terms and conditions</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Any changes to our privacy will be sent out as a  notification through E-mail to our users</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Policy Version: March 21, 2013</span></p>
